relation: Darrow3 - #08 Not one to be left behind, Jeff throws his hat into the ring and reveals a trump card of his own.
Darrow3 - #09 Ness makes a mad dash for the Mani-Mani in an attempt to bring the battle to an end. With Jeff's support, can he land that final strike?

Darrow3 - #10 With the help of his friends, Ness swings down on the Mani-Mani, which has been hidden within the illusion of Giygas. This single blow is all it takes to make the nightmarish form disappear and bring an end to Moonside.
Darrow3 - #11 The return to the real world proves to be a happy occasion, though the troubles Ness and Jeff must face are far from over.
Darrow3 - #12 Remember, the next time you attempt to microwave a burrito, make sure you are not accidentally activating a nuclear device. It happens more often than you may think.
